{"tid":2388233,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【殺出血路】黃圈生意多元化 搶攻飲食零售","createTime":"2021-01-31T03:21:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T03:50:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4578b7f21e4de40b50577709c1c48f96d987e2fe","tid":2388233,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T03:21:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210131/TZBYGNUFCBDRTDOTCIYP73NEBE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210131%2FTZBYGNUFCBDRTDOTCIYP73NEBE%2F&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWtmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=a9d5463a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210131%2FTZBYGNUFCBDRTDOTCIYP73NEBE%2F&h=7b4fb162\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210131/TZBYGNUFCBDRTDOTCIYP73NEBE/</a><br />\n<br />\n【殺出血路】黃圈生意多元化 搶攻飲食零售<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3rzNKEoYuXn-L_77IJ1U09GHrEE=/1000x829/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NFUHO4CDNJBHLJT7UZDJNYMECU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3rzNKEoYuXn-L_77IJ1U09GHrEE%3D%2F1000x829%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNFUHO4CDNJBHLJT7UZDJNYMECU.jpg&h=01b10c54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王宗堯 力谷黃色經濟<br />\n<br />\n當藝人表明立場後，未必如一般對「政治冷感」的藝人所想，從此前途盡失，相反黃色藝人打造的經濟圈，雖受到百般阻攔，但只要同路人互相扶持，總可走出一條謙卑而有骨氣的新天地。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【翻版阿嬌】撐反送中做前線急救被跟蹤<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n王宗堯 力谷黃色經濟<br />\n<br />\n官非纏身的王宗堯一直沒忘記回饋同路人，因龐大律師費開支而公開求懲罰後，他更成為多個黃圈產品代言人，而為保持黃色經濟圈活躍度，王宗堯亦有跟抵抗藍圈yuu消費計劃的Mee合作，並趁新年化身財神推銷「賀年廣告套餐」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/HmMDo218U9jNuIhU-qNb8dmSm8U=/640x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NUNMGPPFT5DJREFMLPIKMGS2SY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHmMDo218U9jNuIhU-qNb8dmSm8U%3D%2F640x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNUNMGPPFT5DJREFMLPIKMGS2SY.jpg&h=e488810e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n杜汶澤 自家點播平台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n杜汶澤 自家點播平台<br />\n<br />\n原本於YouTube和Facebook經營網台節目「喱騷」的杜汶澤，早前宣佈自設收費平台，大搞自家節目，一直主張黃色藝人互相支持意念的他，去年尾更宣佈正式簽下王宗堯，成為網台首位包薪合約藝人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/J6eqhhRQnpAgoK9CKWd3Dr2LMLE=/640x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/P4KYUUP6LJEJ5CCDVAW4VI2YFY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJ6eqhhRQnpAgoK9CKWd3Dr2LMLE%3D%2F640x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FP4KYUUP6LJEJ5CCDVAW4VI2YFY.jpg&h=93833e55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小環渣哥 營業額撐星火<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小環渣哥 營業額撐星火<br />\n<br />\n譚小環轉行跟丈夫渣哥全力投身飲食業，在2019年的社會運動上表態，大渣哥飲食店更多次輔助有需要的年輕人，當時發起的「三罷行動」，渣哥更把三間小食店營業額，不扣除任何營運成本全數撥捐星火基金。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Qq0oTnGci4wFS1cv8kOEVWjsimM=/640x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7MD2K4GNTRGGLJCS62FKFENX34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQq0oTnGci4wFS1cv8kOEVWjsimM%3D%2F640x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7MD2K4GNTRGGLJCS62FKFENX34.jpg&h=57e9082b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吳日言 販售日式飯糰<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n吳日言 販售日式飯糰<br />\n<br />\n吳日言退出娛樂圈變作人妻，更開設販售飯糰等日式食品的小食店，難得於疫情下生意不但撐得住，更大膽地逆巿擴充搶佔巿場。藝人出身的她勇於發聲，於過去的社會運動，甚至身體力行上街遊行，表達訴求。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6FFZwO8yShupRdDqjbDlXfwzHeo=/640x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RPY2SJEVXVAQXLTZ4ZA5AIPIYM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6FFZwO8yShupRdDqjbDlXfwzHeo%3D%2F640x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRPY2SJEVXVAQXLTZ4ZA5AIPIYM.jpg&h=a25c64c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n袁彌明 生活百貨暢旺<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n袁彌明 生活百貨暢旺<br />\n<br />\n袁彌明黃藍絲共冶一爐，她跟與父親袁弓夷大膽直言，並曾高調參與政治活動，2012年與2016年更參選香港立法會選舉，高調作政治表態，但她從政前成立專注有機及護膚的生活百貨店，仍低調地運作，到現時全球更共有10間實體店。"},{"pid":"8704734fd10d4d6715e4e2c986825b9c724c1a95","tid":2388233,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T03:27:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e506bca97272553d9f6e21ff54bebd3cdff4f147","tid":2388233,"uid":150930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T03:29:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><p class=\"left\"></p>"},{"pid":"855659d047ddd1a48d61326f5b2aeca16efb9973","tid":2388233,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T03:29:55.000Z","msg":"渣狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78bcdfdf9d9f85be6bdd0f729adf17e430c31f9f","tid":2388233,"uid":240004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T03:50:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}